Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:06.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Work! Work!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.75,0:00:11.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever catches the fugitive, Velveno,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.41,0:00:18.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,shall receive 4,000,000 jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:24.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! I'm broke right now, \Nso that totally fits the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:56.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just up to you to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:03.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we need the dough, too, so why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This Velveno is an escaped convict
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:08.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that Gray set out to catch \Na long time ago, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:12.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although if I recall right, the reward \Nat the time was 400,000 jewel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.91,0:02:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've gotten valuable \Nthese past seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:17.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the client?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It says Count Balsamico...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:22.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a sour name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.92,0:02:24.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like balsamic vinegar!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:26.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Balsamico?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:29.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I heard that Velveno \Nguy is gonna show up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.63,0:02:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Balsamico family's magical ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:41.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ball that's held once every seven \Nyears and only wizards can attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:43.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's next Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:48.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go to the ball \Nand capture Velveno!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm gettin' fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's head out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:54.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.50,0:03:00.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna participate in a ball, \Nyou'll have to practice dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:11.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start with the basic steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, hold my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, this is a pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are Natsu-nii and Lucy-nee trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.61,0:03:24.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Social dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Social dancing? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:30.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a game where you \Nstep on each other's feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's the aim...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:41.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Social dancing is where a man and \Nwoman pair up and dance at a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a fun game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You just disqualified yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:58.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray-sama is going to dance \Nflirtatiously behind Juvia's back...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:02.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it means being able to dance with \NGray-sama, Juvia will strip, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was once known as the "Dancing Demon",
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.03,0:04:08.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so if you want to learn social \Ndancing, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:09.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Natsu! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses! Dancing is all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:19.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...fighting spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.87,0:04:23.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna throw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anybody who dances with Erza always \Ngets sick to their stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:30.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can see why she was \Ncalled the "Dancing Demon".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to be the one \Nwho teaches Natsu how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:36.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm gonna take a little break...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, Natsu! Let your shoulders relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:47.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How can an adult be that delicate?! \NAnd you call yourself a Man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman, you're up next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:54.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A Man... gets sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this social dancing? It's lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:10.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! Wendy's great at dancing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:12.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why is she dancing with Warren?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.54,0:05:15.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's you and me try dancing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! It looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:28.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you give me the honor \Nof a dance, young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.32,0:05:33.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard! Taking advantage of \Nthis chaos is playin' dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:35.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:37.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:39.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I ain't gonna dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:44.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nobody's asking you to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Levy, dance with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! I said it first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:52.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:57.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice if you're \Ngonna be like that about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I didn't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to dance, I'm the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.28,0:06:06.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Visitar, your dances are \Nsomething else entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To be frank, you're just in the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:12.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This has become a big fuss \Nright under my nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:17.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But... somewhere along the \Nline, I lost my partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You called?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I sure didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh... You're really good at dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:26.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a member of the Heartfilia family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:30.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you need to be raised as a \Nproper lady, Lucy-sama. Thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. But I think this \Nis a little overkill...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:37.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That matters not. Let's take \Nit from the top once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:48.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Balsamico \NPalace, home of the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:54.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So the magical ball's gonna \Nbe held in this palace, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:56.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It was farther away than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.78,0:06:59.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be helped. We're \Ndoing it for the dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have tagged along \Nif you're only doing it to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:06.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask who you people are?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:09.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a real dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to mentally shout that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Aceto, daughter of Balsamico, \Nlord of this palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a name you'd probably \Nbite your tongue saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Natsu of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:30.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've accepted the request \Nof your father, the Count.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:32.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll show you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:42.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Count Balsamico, the client.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not only got a sour name...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His face is sour, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clam it, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:54.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting down to business, it's \Na little more complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:56.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,than what I wrote in the request.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:07:57.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us hear the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the apple of my \Neye, my beautiful daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:04.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name again? Tonguebite-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aceto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:09.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies. Please continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:14.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, my daughter's husband will be \Ndecided at this evening's magical ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Her husband?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:21.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For that purpose, I've got a ring that \Nonly comes out once every seven years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:23.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious ring that \Nthe Balsamico family
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,has handed down from \Ngeneration to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:29.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Velveno has his eye on the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:34.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. In truth, Velveno went after \Nthe ring seven years ago, but failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:38.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, though, the husband \Nselection process was ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.90,0:08:42.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But with a face like this, even disguised,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.94,0:08:45.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't Velveno be easy to catch \Nif he tried to sneak into the ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:49.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He uses Transformation \NMagic and Magical Drain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magical Drain? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:57.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a truly troublesome form of magic \Nthat lets him copy the magic powers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,of whatever wizard he touches \Nfor a short period of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:02.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! That ain't too shabby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:07.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to combine your powers \Nand protect the ring from Velveno!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then capture the scoundrel \Nand send him back to prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got you covered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.72,0:09:16.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you down, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:19.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And just to make sure, if we catch Velveno,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:21.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll follow through with what \Nwas written on the request form...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:25.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I'll pay 4,000,000 jewel in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesss!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cash! Right when I need it the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect-ebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I'm so cute that \Nsomebody proposes to {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:44.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:48.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in serious mode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:51.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Work or not, this is the \Nminimum amount of decorum due
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:52.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when participating in a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy, you look super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:02.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a little embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:07.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! The ball's curtain is going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.10,0:10:09.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting up on stage, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:13.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza is into this as much \Nas she was acting that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll do my best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:19.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But first I have to cast Troia on Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren, anyone here seem \Nlike they could be Velveno?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:32.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I used a surveillance lacrima \Nto investigate the whole place,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no sign of him at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:38.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let you know the second \Nwe spot a suspicious character!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Until then, try to act naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are Natsu and the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy and the others are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't we blend in with \Nthe other guests and dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's... Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you nervous about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:02.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, is Velveno really going to \Nshow up at a glitzy place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:06.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is look for a suspicious \Nguy without ruffling any feathers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:10.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:15.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No frownin' now! C'mon, cut the rug with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:19.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some suspicious guy just \Ninvited Erza to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Check him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:30.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That the guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is spinning! \NI mean, more than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have enough spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,About Erza, we, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:41.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't have to worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.69,0:11:44.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now someone asked Lucy to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's suspiciously good-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should check him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So Lucy's next...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you won't take "no" for an answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:03.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...we have no choice but to dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:09.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll handle this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have this dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! This is what a Man is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:18.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy I was born a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:22.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fishy for a beautiful woman \Nlike that to go up to Elfman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.37,0:12:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's Velveno, she probably intends \Nto drain Elfman's Beast Soul power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman who asked Elfman \Nto dance is suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How dreamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Elfman! Let Gray take over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:12:59.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:03.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're in love, the bigger the \Nobstacle, the more fired up you become!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:05.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is precisely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...a Man!     {"what a Man is" better grammar, but I don't think Elfman cares about syntax}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a new partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a pretty nice-looking guy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:19.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Being a guest here at the magical ball \Nmust mean you're a wizard, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of magic can you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Before asking a lady about magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:28.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it's proper for a gentleman to say \Nwhat kind of magic he does first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:32.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I have no \Ninterest in being a gentleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:36.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? In that case, I'll show you mine first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:39.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:43.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She uses the same kind of \NIce Make Magic that I use?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Kite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.91,0:13:58.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Polar Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:03.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.44,0:14:08.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love when it gets intense like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too! Ice Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:17.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:27.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like things have gotten \Nout of hand, as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aceto-san has come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:15:00.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aceto, it seems that you're so beautiful, \Nno one dares ask you for a dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.62,0:15:04.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dazzling beauty is too Manly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:09.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. May I have this dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Why is Erza dancing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:19.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Would you care to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.38,0:15:30.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is that little kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's way too young for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.10,0:15:34.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's over at midnight \Nand it's nearly that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It begins at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What begins?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:51.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The unveiling of the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:56.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That giant grandfather's clock \Nonly opens once every seven years,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:15:58.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,releasing a device that displays the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:02.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And following Balsamico family \Ntradition, whatever man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:07.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,can obtain the ring from there has \Nthe right to propose to my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.68,0:16:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who gets the ring...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:17.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll investigate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:24.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Those of you men who would propose \Nto my daughter, go for that ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Man, propose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:32.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What would you even do if you proposed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy Wendy was dancing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:44.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guy with an afro grabbed \Nme right before I came in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:46.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Velveno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:49.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the person who's with Wendy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:53.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy! That guy is Velveno!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Transformation Cancellation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:03.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Sky Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:14.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all witnessed me, Velveno, \Ntaking the Balsamico ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.87,0:17:16.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Velveno...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Return that ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is finally getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:22.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:28.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Dragon's Roar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were all dancing, \NI drained your power, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your opponent is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:51.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gray! Elfman! Keep Aceto-dono safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:53.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:54.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:58.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip! Purgatory Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:01.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip! Purgatory Armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:12.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already copied the magic of \Nevery member of Fairy Tail here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.58,0:18:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect! I've always wanted \Nto throw down with a copycat,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:20.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,just to see how far he can take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there, boss. I didn't come \Nhere tonight to brawl with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.79,0:18:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I failed last time, but have waited \Npatiently these seven years...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...to propose to you, Aceto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.99,0:18:41.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Propose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:45.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been chums ever since we were kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but I've always been madly in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:54.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I allowed you, the son of a servant, \Nto be my daughter's playmate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:56.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten that debt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:19:00.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since you drove me out of the \Nmansion, I came back again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to visit Aceto, but every time, you used \Nthe difference in our social positions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,as an excuse to turn me away at the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:09.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, I never heard about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:12.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind! Hush your mouth, daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:16.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For a while, I accepted your \Nreasoning and gave up on Aceto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:22.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But because of that, my heart grew \Nwild, I got involved in crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and before I knew it, ended up in prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.05,0:19:28.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he goin' on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.49,0:19:29.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:37.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But every minute I was in jail, I regretted \Nnot letting you know how I felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:40.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I broke out, so \NI could take this chance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that only comes around \Nonce every seven years!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the second time for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:56.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aceto, be my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.85,0:20:00.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How romantic...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course she refuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:17.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aceto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:21.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Velveno, I've been waiting \Nall this time for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.33,0:20:22.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:26.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll really become my wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:27.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Except...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to turn yourself in \Nand pay for your crimes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:46.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a fairy tale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:51.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.95,0:20:54.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's being a Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:58.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wish these two luck \Nwith a round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:11.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:13.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that I'll wait for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. And I swear I'll come back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:25.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... About the reward...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:29.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'm gonna pay it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I say we dance \Nthe rest of the night away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:34.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,to pray for Aceto-dono's happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:46.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a way for it to turn out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope someone proposes \Nto me like that someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.77,0:21:57.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:00.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:06.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate so much I'm bloated, so I'm goin' home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:07.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:12.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't be like that! Hang \Nout a little longer with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:20.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,1-2-3! 1-2-3! Stop stepping on my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Troia ran out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:25.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Let me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:24:00.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, when are you gonna get \Nused to transportation, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:03.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I warned against this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:07.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew this job would involve having \Nto get on some transportation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.00,0:24:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's happening? It looks like \Nthe whole world is spinning!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:13.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the world that's \Nspinning, Natsu, it's your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.84,0:24:16.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: The Truly Evil Jiggle Butt Gang!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.79,0:24:18.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! B-Butt...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.86,0:24:20.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Your behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:21.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.30,0:24:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Butt... My butt is spinning, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.96,0:24:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
